7:
Sir! Commander Suzukaze, reporting
for duty!
10:
As announced earlier, we have been
tasked with investigating the
mysterious disappearances.
12:
The diviners will not tolerate any
delay. We each have a part to play
in clearing our names in this matter!
19:
Suzukaze, your task is to deal with
the fugitive ninja involved in the
disappearances.
21:
The law of ninja is absolute—the
sentence for defectors is death.
Execute without hesitation.
36:
There's absolutely NO way I'm cut
out for this! I mean, it was a total
fluke I ended up commander
anyway!
37:
Besides, it's the diviners' job to look
into this kind of stuff! Why'd us ninjas
get saddled with work too?
43:
And this whole fugitive business...
Forget offing the other person, I'm
totally dying first!
47:
We're talking about a child prodigy
here—the same one that blew up an
entire village! I'm deader than dead
if I pick a fight!
52:
Grr... Those big wigs probably just
needed a convenient sacrifice so
they don't lose any more of the
good ninjas...
55:
*sniff* Why, oh why, was I born a
ninja?
64: You've got to be kidding me!
109:
Ohmigosh, a-a-a real yokai? Please
don't eat me—I'm too young to die!
113:
And give myself an upset stomach?
No thanks.
116: That's Nimbus. I don't think he's yokai.
120:
Hello, and welcome to Starview
Village.
125:
Oh, uh, nice to... meet you? I'm
Suzuka.
128:
And where exactly is this Starview
Village? I think I got spirited away
here somehow...
132:
No need to panic. I assume you hail
from Yamato, judging by your
clothes. We can send you home in
no time.
137:
(This thing can send me places?
Does he know something about the
disappearances? He's sus! TOTALLY
sus!)
145:
Oh no, my head hurts a ton! I can't...
remember who I am!
154:
That's right! Oh, woe is me! I have no
memories!
158:
I wouldn't have anywhere to go,
even if you sent me to the East. I'd
rather stay here with you guys.
163:
Promise I can be helpful! I've lived by
myself for so long, I can do house
chores blindfolded!
167:
I'm in pretty good shape too!
Whatever you need, I'm your girl!
171:
You know you lived by yourself a
while, huh? What happened to
losing your memories?
176:
U-uh, I only meant that as a gut
feeling! I don't actually remember!
180:
You mentioned the East without us
saying anything... You SURE you're
not a ninja from there?
198:
Maybe we should just bring her to
the Diviners' Commission and let
them deal with this.
204:
The commission?! Now h-hold on
just a moment there! Please don't
take me to those meanies!
207: Let me stay here... I'll do anything...
215: Surely you see how suspicious she is.
217:
Regardless, I am capable of
monitoring her.
221:
She's not a bad person either...
probably.
224:
(Rather, she's so bad at keeping
secrets I doubt we have anything to
worry about.)
228:
All right... We keep an eye on her for
the time being then.
232:
We will be watching your every
move, Suzuka.
237:
H-hooray? Thank you so much!
Promise you won't regret it!
